========================================
TASKS OF THE DAY
========================================

1) UNDERSTAND THE DATA
----------------------
- Data is text-heavy, structured, academic.
- Very suitable for RAG.
- Needs structured chunking + handling of tables/figures.
- No OCR complexity.
- Must maintain logical flow using headings.
- Embedding model must perform well on long academic text.


