3) DIFFERENT EMBEDDING MODELS

------------------------------------------------------------
1. OPEN-SOURCE (SELF-HOST FOR FREE)
------------------------------------------------------------
These models are free to download and run on our own infrastructure.
They offer maximum cost control (infinite longevity) but require some setup.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Model Name                        | Key Strength                                                                | Dimensions | Max Seq Length  | Hosting / Access
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BAAI/bge-base-en-v1.5             | Top English retrieval. High performance on MTEB. Excellent for RAG.         | 768        | 512             | Hugging Face / Ollama
intfloat/e5-base-v2               | Balanced, robust, high accuracy-speed tradeoff. Multi-domain performance.   | 768        | 512             | Hugging Face / Ollama
all-MiniLM-L6-v2                  | Fastest & smallest. Lightweight. Great baseline embedding model.            | 384        | 256             | Hugging Face / Ollama
EmbeddingGemma-300M               | Lightweight multilingual. Efficient for limited hardware.                   | 1024       | 512             | Hugging Face


------------------------------------------------------------
2. API-BASED (FREE TIER ACCESS)
------------------------------------------------------------
Models hosted by their providers; we access them through an API.

Model Name                     | Key Strength                                                            | Dimensions | Max Seq Length | Free API Status
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gemini Embedding               | Simple API. Works perfectly with Gemini LLMs. Multimodal support.      | 768        | 2048           | FREE (High limits)
OpenAI text-embedding-3-small  | Industry standard. Highly optimized. Great reliability.                | 1536       | 8192           | Paid (No free tier)


------------------------------------------------------------
RAG MODEL SELECTION ADVICE
------------------------------------------------------------

For academic PDFs (dense + technical material):

Fastest API Development:
- Use the Gemini Embedding model.
- Best pairing: Gemini 2.5 Flash (Generation) + Gemini Embedding (Retrieval).
- Easiest integration + completely free API access.

Highest Accuracy (Self-Hosted):
- Use BAAI/bge-base-en-v1.5 or intfloat/e5-base-v2.
- These achieve top retrieval accuracy on benchmark datasets.
- Ideal for maximum precision in chatbot answers.
